<b>Healing Light</b>: At 1st level, you gain the ability to channel celestial energy to heal wounds. You have a pool of d6s that you spend to fuel this healing. The number of dice in the pool equals 1 + your warlock level. As a bonus action, you can heal one creature you can see within 60' of you, spending dice from the pool. The maximum number of dice you can spend at once equals your Charisma modifier (minimum 1). Roll the dice you spend, add them together, and restore a number of hit points equal to the total. Your pool regains all dice when you finish a long rest.<p>
<b>Amorphous Ooze</b>: You can move through a space as narrow as 1 inch wide without squeezing.  You can return to your natural ooze form as an action, or other gelatinous forms as well.<p>

